{"tid":1724443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位和理非文宣組手足入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-15T12:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T18:42:48.000Z","uid":121435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2b5bdb20cb3767d5b1b217761074fd407636bc","tid":1724443,"uid":121435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"其實呢一個星期都開始堆積咗好大嘅民怨<br />\n政府想用佢地打民意戰<br />\n點解我地唔做好文宣 將矛頭直指返政府<br />\n打個比如<br />\n打風個天落雨落到水浸返唔到工D人都會屌尻天文台唔掛八號波<br />\n你返唔到工點解唔係屌尻政府無能而係將責任推卸落示威者？<br />\n落雨落到水浸你唔去屌尻個天點解要打風？<br />\n明明政府應該負上最大責任 到呢刻果班狗官仲係覺得自己完全無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085c37d52df252e0c2281bfff2b53f33475e3d70","tid":1724443,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d197c4c46627f1c7cbbabce903d122a30f95b679","tid":1724443,"uid":121435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe52b1db630db4e7ff4014fbbf0cfc4a14ce8a43","tid":1724443,"uid":121435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f127a5a4613239994b0ba0f6afceb62eb68af8b5","tid":1724443,"uid":221336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"085c37d52df252e0c2281bfff2b53f33475e3d70","tid":1724443,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"580714cce840deec852c3905853c4b4c4fb57f73","tid":1724443,"uid":264773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:27:35.000Z","msg":"文宣重點：<br />\nCs 二惡英危害+恐怖圖 for 中立+自私藍<br />\n周同學 for 淺黃，support 升級嘅正當性"},{"pid":"303007071865c71f1796f8256eba959566f6dd4e","tid":1724443,"uid":221336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5xEvNh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu